It's not everyday that you see a VW legend in a revving competition with a Porsche. The VW VR6 engine has been hailed as one of the greatest engines ever made by the company, in South Africa the engines were used in the Jetta MK3 and the Gold MK3. These two cars were loved so mush that to date, they still hold a special place in Mzansi's petrol-head's hearts. In this video that has gone viral, a man who was busy washing the VR6 can be seen revving the car after hearing the sound of the Porsche.